full_text: OMB 115-0052 U. S. Department of Justice Screened by NARA, 9/21/2023 Expires 9/30/84 Immigration and Naturalization Service Notice of Final Naturalization Hearing Naturalization and Citizenship Branch File or A # 21 207 655 300 NORTH LOS ANGELES STREET Date 4/03/1983 LOS ANGELES, CA 90012 Petition # 480603 You are hereby notified to appear for a hearing on your petition for naturalization before a judge of the naturalization court at the DATE, TIME, AND PLACE, SHOWN BELOW. Date 4/22/1983 Time 12:00 MD BACHCHI THI TRAN 5028 COYOTE LANE SAN BERNARDINO, CA 92407 Place PASADENA CITY COLLEGE - ADM BLDG 1570 E COLORADO PASADENA, CA 91106 ROOM: SEXSON AUDITORIUM You must bring the following with you: This letter, with all of the QUESTIONS ON THE REVERSE side answered in ink or on a typewriter. - Alien Registration Card. - Rentry Permit, or Refugee Travel Document. - Any Immigration documents you may have. - If the naturalization hearing is ON BEHALF OF YOUR CHILD (children), BRING your CHILD (children). If you cannot come to this hearing, return this notice immediately and state why you cannot appear. In such case, please use the return address in the extreme upper left hand corner of this letter. You will be sent another notice of hearing at a later date. Form N-445A- IMPORTANT - PLEASE SEE REVERSE
